spec_data.Name: php-horde-Horde-Image
spec_data.Description:
An Image utility API, with backends for:
* GD
* GIF
* PNG
* SVG
* SWF
* ImageMagick convert command line tool
* Imagick Extension

Optional dependency: php-pecl-imagick
